WEBVTT

00:06:56.240 --> 00:07:00.216
Something he had lived without
for three decades.

00:07:00.240 --> 00:07:03.696
When he arrived with little more
than the clothes on his back,

00:07:03.720 --> 00:07:05.176
he found everything:

00:07:05.200 --> 00:07:08.776
from a toaster, Crock-Pot and stove

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:12.200
to a toothbrush and toothpaste
awaiting for him.

00:07:13.040 --> 00:07:14.880
He describes it simply

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:17.040
as heaven.

00:07:18.680 --> 00:07:20.320
On the other side of the world,

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:23.016
I listened to Antoinette,

00:07:23.040 --> 00:07:25.856
the director of this
training and community center

00:07:25.880 --> 00:07:28.296
for women in rural Rwanda.

00:07:28.320 --> 00:07:31.816
Hundreds of women
come to this place daily --